scene.message:
Nanjo: Listen up, Inaba!{nl}
Don't touch anything{nl}
suspicious ahead!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Kandori...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Oh, sorry — never mind.{nl}
Let's keep moving!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Of all the nerve —{nl}
building this stuff{nl}
in our studio!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Of all the nerve!{nl}
I liked this place —{nl}
now it's totally ruined!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: With this bunch,{nl}
the tension level is{nl}
seriously lacking...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hey, {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Stop wandering around!{waitkey}We need to find Kandori{nl}
before he does{nl}
more damage.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I've always been{nl}
interested in SEBEC.{nl}
Can't wait to see inside!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Where are you going?{nl}
The enemy is inside{nl}
SEBEC,I believe...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I'll take{nl}
the lead,okay?{waitkey}{nl}
No point in the leader{nl}
hogging the spotlight.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey,{nl}
Kandori didn't escape{nl}
outside, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}I know you'd want to run,{nl}
but this is the moment —{nl}
up front, let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Are we really{nl}
going? Can't we just...{nl}
not?{waitkey}{ret}
